玫耳分佈在[[環北帶|環北帶]]<ref name=Redhead1989/>，包括[[加拿大|加拿大]]<ref name=Redhead1989/><ref name="urlRhodotus palmatus">{{cite web|url=http://www.usask.ca/biology/fungi/genus_species_pages/rhodotus_palmatus.shtml|author=Kaminskyj S|publisher=University of Saskatchewan|title=''Rhodotus palmatus''|accessdate=2009-06-14|archive-date=2008-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509192415/http://www.usask.ca/biology/fungi/genus_species_pages/rhodotus_palmatus.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[伊朗|伊朗]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Saber M|year=1990|title=Contribution to the knowledge of Agaricales pleurotoid in habit in Iran|journal=Iranian Journal of Plant Pathology|volume=26|issue=1–4|pages=29–40}}</ref>、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Siller I|year=1999|title=Rare macrofungi in the Kekes north forest reserve in the Matra mountains, Hungary|journal=Mikologiai Kozlemenyek|volume=38|issue=1/3|pages=11–24|language=hu}}</ref>、[[義大利|義大利]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Migliozzi V, Coccia M|year=1998|title=Fungi from lazio area. IX. 43–46|journal=Micologia Italiana|volume=27|issue=3|pages=25–36|language=it}}</ref>、[[波蘭|波蘭]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Bujakiewicz A, Nita J|year=2004|title=Żyłkowiec różowawy ''Rhodotus palmatus'' (Bull.: Fr.) R. Maire – mieszkaniec białowieskich ostępów|journal=Chrońmy Przyrodę Ojczystą|volume=60|issue=5|pages=82–85|language=pl}}</ref>、[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Ripkova S|year=2003|title=New, rare and less known macromycetes in Slovakia I|journal=Czech Mycology|volume=55|issue=3–4|pages=187–200}}</ref>、[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[挪威|挪威]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Vesterholt J.|year=2005|title=Notes on rare fungi collected in Denmark|journal=Svampe|volume=55|pages=24–38}}</ref>、[[德國|德國]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Krieglsteiner GJ|year=1979|title=1st reports of Ascomycetes and Basidiomycetes in West Germany|journal=Zeitschrift für Mykologie|volume=45|issue=1|pages=35–44|language=de}}</ref>、以往[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的地區<ref name="Singer1986"/>、[[韓國|韓國]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Han S-K, Park Y-J, Choi S-K, Lee J-O, Choi J-H, Sung J-M.|year=2006|title=Some unrecorded higher fungi of the Seoraksan and Odaesan National Parks|journal=Mycobiology|volume=34|issue=2|pages=56–60}}</ref>、[[日本|日本]]<ref name=Redhead1989>{{cite journal en|last=Redhead SA|year=1989|title=A biogeographical overview of the Canadian mushroom flora|journal=Canadian Journal of Botany|volume=67|pages=3003–62|doi=10.1139/b89-384}}</ref>及[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]。<ref>{{cite book en|title=New Zealand Fungi: An Illustrated Guide|last=Stevenson G|year=1994|publisher=Canterbury University Press|location=Christchurch, New Zealand|id=ISBN 978-0908812295|page=56}}</ref>玫耳在美國分佈在[[印地安納州|印地安納州]]<ref>{{cite journal en|last= Cooke WB|year=1975|title=The 1970 Indiana foray|journal=Mycologia|volume=67|issue=5|pages=1065–71}}</ref>及[[北美洲|北美洲]]其他東部地區。<ref name=Miller2006/>雖然玫耳較為罕有，但在[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]卻較普遍。<ref name=Sundberg1997>{{cite journal en|last=Sundberg WJ, Methven AS, Monoson HL|year=1997|title=''Rhodotus palmatus'' (Basidiomycetes, Agaricales, Tricholomataceae) in Illinois|journal=Mycotaxon|volume=65|pages=403–10|url=http://194.203.77.76/LibriFungorum/Image.asp?ItemID=283&ImageFileName=0403b.jpg|accessdate=11-09-2009}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>有指由於[[榆樹|榆樹]]因[[荷蘭榆樹病|荷蘭榆樹病]]而枯竭增加，卻令玫耳有復甦的跡象。<ref name=McIlvainea2007/><ref>{{cite journal en|last=Dobson FS, Hawksworth DL|year=1995/6|title=The Slapton fungal (including lichen) survey: inventorying and documenting changes in the Mycobiota|journal=Field Studies|volume=8|issue=4|pages=677–84|format=PDF|url=http://www.field-studies-council.org/fieldstudies/documents/vol8.4_235.pdf|accessdate=2009-09-22|issn=0428-304X|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090509042932/http://www.field-studies-council.org/fieldstudies/documents/vol8.4_235.pdf|archive-date=2009-05-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===照明===
近紅光的[[可見光|可見光]]是玫耳生長所需的光譜，這與一般[[真菌|真菌]]所需的藍光有所不同。<ref name=Miller1980/>在[[波長|波長]]500納米以上的紅光、黃光或綠光下，玫耳都可以結出[[子實體|子實體]]；若只有藍光，則不能長成。玫耳的[[顯型|顯型]]會受到照明的顏色及光度所影響。例如在綠光下，子實體會呈淡橙色，[[蕈柄|蕈柄]]較短及筆直，[[傘狀帽|傘狀帽]]很大及有明顯的紋；這與在綠葉下長成的玫耳相像。若是在黃光照射下，玫耳會呈鮮橙色，傘狀帽較細小，紋理也不明顯；這與在冬天落葉後長成的玫耳相似。<ref name=Miller1980>{{cite journal en|last=Miller OK Jr, Palmer JG, Gillman LS|year=1980|title=The fruiting and development of ''Rhodotus palmatus'' in culture|journal=Mycotaxon|volume=11|issue=2|pages=409–19}}</ref>

==保育狀況==
[[image:Rhodotus_palmatus1.jpg|thumb]]
1980年代的[[歐洲|歐洲]]因[[空氣污染|空氣污染]]及改變土地用途，[[真菌|真菌]]的數量大幅下降。自此歐洲多國就對真菌的[[生物多樣性|生物多樣性]]進行研究，並制訂了真菌的紅色名錄。<ref>{{cite book en|title=Guidance for Conservation of Macrofungi in Europe|last=Senn-Irlet B, Heilmann-Clausen J, Genny D, Dahlberg A|year=2007|publisher=European Council for the Conservation of Fungi|location=Strasborg|url=http://www.wsl.ch/eccf/Guidance_Fungi.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2009-09-13|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716064512/http://www.wsl.ch/eccf/Guidance_Fungi.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>玫耳在超過一半的歐洲國家中都被列入紅色名錄，狀況屬於[[極危|極危]]、[[瀕危|瀕危]]或[[近危|近危]]。<ref>{{cite book en|title=European Red List of endangered macrofungi: Red list candidates|last=Dahlberg A|year=2007|publisher=European Council for the Conservation of Fungi|format=Excel file|url=http://www.wsl.ch/eccf/candlist-subtotals.xls Excel file|accessdate=2009-09-13|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716064417/http://www.wsl.ch/eccf/candlist-subtotals.xls|dead-url=no}}</ref>玫耳在[[愛沙尼亞|愛沙尼亞]]、[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]及[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]已經出現區域性[[滅絕|滅絕]]。<ref name="isbn2-8317-0161-9">{{cite book en|author=IUCN East European Programme|title=Environmental status reports|publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature and Natural Resources|location=Cambridge|year=1991|page=198|id=ISBN 2-8317-0161-9}}</ref>它們是[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]受保護的35種真菌之一，任何採集都是違法的。<ref>{{cite journal en|last= Siller I, Dima B, Albert L, Vasas G, Fodor L, Pal-Fam F, Bratek Z, Zagyva I|year=2006|title=Vedett nagygombafajok Magyarorszagon|trans_title=Protected macrofungi in Hungary|journal=Mikologiai Kozlemenyek|volume=45|issue=1/3|pages=3–158|language=hu,en}}</ref>

